      "content": "it doesn't feel temporary though. it feels like its just who i am now. how am i supposed to look my parents in the eye? or my employees who lost their jobs because of my bad calls? everyone expects me to have it figured out and now i'm just a walking disaster. there's no \"way forward\" when you're starting from negative millions. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to not have to feel this way anymore.",
